messages.message: If its a champion we are building at an enterprise customer, I don’t want them to have to put their CC details in if they use their credits up. We want them to get as excited as possible so that we can sell them large enterprise deals.
Discussed this with Anant. His guidance is to support it on a case by case basis, with approval by GTM leaders and Anant. I’ll shoot out a note on this to the field teams.
